<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Account Warning — <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f13;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 0 0 32px; }
    .logo-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
      border-radius: 8px; font-size: 18px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .logo-text { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #fcd34d; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #141420 0%, #1a1710 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1c1500 0%, #2d2000 50%, #1c1500 100%);
      padding: 48px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 200px; height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .warn-icon {
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706, #92400e);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      font-size: 38px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(245,158,11,0.5), 0 0 80px rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 15px; color: #fcd34d; line-height: 1.6; }
    .content { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .greeting strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
    /* Warning message box */
    .warning-box {
      background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3);
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .warning-box-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .warning-box-header span { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24; letter-spacing: 0.8px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .warning-message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #fde68a;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    /* What happens next */
    .next-steps {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .step-item {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .step-icon { font-size: 18px; min-width: 26px; margin-top: 1px; }
    .step-text { font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }
    .step-text strong { color: #cbd5e1; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .cta-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 8px; }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b45309, #d97706);
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(245,158,11,0.35);
    }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(245,158,11,0.15), transparent); margin: 32px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 0 40px 32px; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; }
    .footer a { color: #f59e0b; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo-badge">
        <div class="logo-icon">💬</div>
        <span class="logo-text"><%= appName %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="warn-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1>Account Warning</h1>
        <p>You have received an official warning on your account, <%= name %>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p class="greeting">
          Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,<br /><br />
          Our administrative team has issued an <strong>official warning</strong> on your 
          <strong><%= appName %></strong> account. Please read the message below carefully and 
          take appropriate action to avoid further consequences.
        </p>

        <!-- Warning message block -->
        <div class="warning-box">
          <div class="warning-box-header">
            <span>⚠️ &nbsp;Admin Warning Message</span>
          </div>
          <p class="warning-message">"<%= warningMessage %>"</p>
        </div>

        <div class="next-steps">
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-icon">📖</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Review your activity</strong>
              Evaluate any recent actions that may have caused this warning and cease them immediately.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Read the Terms of Service</strong>
              Ensure you are fully familiar with our platform guidelines to prevent future violations.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-icon">🤝</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Repeated violations</strong>
              Continued violations after a warning may result in temporary suspension or permanent account removal.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-wrap">
          <a class="cta-btn" href="#">Contact Support →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This warning was issued by a <%= appName %> administrator.<br />
          If you believe this was issued in error, please <a href="#">contact support</a> to dispute it.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 8px;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
